    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Omelet You Cook》是一款疯狂的街机类 roguelike 游戏，考验你的烹饪技能！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291300/extras/e83f63971890b0a164fd9a89d1d09863.poster.avif?t=1771574394\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291300/extras/e83f63971890b0a164fd9a89d1d09863.webm?t=1771574394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291300/extras/e83f63971890b0a164fd9a89d1d09863.mp4?t=1771574394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过组合食材来创造完美的煎蛋卷，以满足古怪顾客不断增长的需求。每一轮都会带来新的挑战、危险、限制以及越来越高的得分门槛，考验你烹饪创意的极限。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291300/extras/24a7310ebd59b9d4d2028ff53438879d.avif?t=1771574394\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个顾客都有独特的个性和口味，所以你需要保持灵活，根据需求随时调整你的食谱。你可能一会儿在做经典的青椒培根煎蛋卷，下一刻又要把甜甜圈、泡菜和菠萝加入其中。保持冷静，把煎蛋卷做出来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Omelet You Cook》由两位独立开发者制作，灵感来源于经典的街机 roguelike 游戏，如《Balatro》、《Luck Be a Landlord》和《Ballionaire》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特点：</strong> 🥄 20+ 种顾客特性，每一轮都不同<br>🥓 40+ 种美味（有时也很荒谬）的食材<br>🥗 几乎无限的食谱组合<br>🥑 可解锁食材和升级<br>🧀 扩展烹饪工具的商店<br>🌶️ 多种难度和初始食材选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你认为自己能成为一名超负荷的食堂阿姨吗？那就来试试吧；煎蛋卷等你做！</p>",
